    {"id":"el19","type":"text","x":75,"y":578,"width":1190,"height":200,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#141a1f","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":1,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"seed":5019,"version":1,"versionNonce":6019,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1700000000000,"link":null,"locked":false,"text":"AUTENTICACIÓN — 3 vías, mismo JWT { sub, role }:\n  1) LDAP bind — personal existente (ana/carlos/maria) ·········· POST /auth/login\n  2) Auto-registro por cédula — nuevo personal, valida contra employees.cedula, rol = employees.cargo · POST /api/staff/register · POST /api/staff/login\n  3) JSON local — invitados de la tienda, sin LDAP ··············· POST /api/guest/register · POST /api/guest/login\n\nAUTORIZACIÓN: roles.json → atencion · rrhh · inventario · administrador (superusuario: todo) · guest\n\nENDPOINTS DE DATOS: GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/:departamento (?q= búsqueda) · GET/PUT /api/pedidos\nGET /api/public/catalog · POST /api/public/orders (checkout) · GET /api/public/orders/mine","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","baseline":15,"containerId":null,"originalText":"AUTENTICACIÓN — 3 vías, mismo JWT { sub, role }:\n  1) LDAP bind — personal existente (ana/carlos/maria) ·········· POST /auth/login\n  2) Auto-registro por cédula — nuevo personal, valida contra employees.cedula, rol = employees.cargo · POST /api/staff/register · POST /api/staff/login\n  3) JSON local — invitados de la tienda, sin LDAP ··············· POST /api/guest/register · POST /api/guest/login\n\nAUTORIZACIÓN: roles.json → atencion · rrhh · inventario · administrador (superusuario: todo) · guest\n\nENDPOINTS DE DATOS: GET/POST/PUT/DELETE /api/:departamento (?q= búsqueda) · GET/PUT /api/pedidos\nGET /api/public/catalog · POST /api/public/orders (checkout) · GET /api/public/orders/mine","lineHeight":1.35},

